### 缓存服务API测试

#### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:3002/api/health

#### 获取IIIF信息
GET http://localhost:3002/api/cache/iiif/info/book_23416

#### 获取IIIF图像
GET http://localhost:3002/api/cache/iiif/region/book_23416/full/400,600/0/default

#### 设置缓存
POST http://localhost:3002/api/cache/set
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "test:key",
  "value": {
    "message": "Hello World",
    "timestamp": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z"
  },
  "ttl": 3600
}

#### 获取缓存
GET http://localhost:3002/api/cache/get/test:key

#### 删除缓存
DELETE http://localhost:3002/api/cache/delete/test:key

#### 批量获取缓存
POST http://localhost:3002/api/cache/mget
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keys": ["test:key1", "test:key2", "test:key3"]
}

#### 清空缓存
POST http://localhost:3002/api/cache/clear
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pattern": "test:*"
}

#### 获取缓存统计
GET http://localhost:3002/api/cache/stats

### AI后端服务API测试

#### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health

#### AI解读
POST http://localhost:3001/api/ai/interpret
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试标题",
  "content": "这是测试内容，用于AI解读功能。",
  "notes": "测试注释",
  "time": "2024-01-01"
}